Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's okay, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're new recruits who heard\Nall about me and came from afar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to join the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to ask a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A favor? Of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! We want a big ship...\N--You, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't appreciate you breaking\Nin here without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Weirdest Guy Ever!\NJango the Hypnotist"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, Klahadore,\Nthese people are--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can wait for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear all about your reasons later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now leave, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, we want a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usopp-kun!\N--Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're well-known in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've been\Non many an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite impressive for\Nsomeone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Captain Usopp, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you admire me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard all about\Nyour father, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but the\Nson of a filthy pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you do will surprise me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I ask that you stay away\Nfrom the lady of this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Filthy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and you are from\Ncompletely different worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it money you're after?\NHow much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Klahadore!\NApologize to Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Be careful, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What reason is there to apologize\Nto this savage man, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am merely stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must truly hate your\Ngreat idiot of a father
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for abandoning his family and village\Nbecause of his lust for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare insult\Nmy father any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting\Nunnecessarily riled up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not simply tell another of\Nyour special lies at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how your father is\Nreally a traveling salesman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or how you're not\Nreally related by blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-See! You immediately\Nresort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like father, like son!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud that my father is a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud that he's a\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I am an exaggerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll never lie about my pride\Nto be related by blood to a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the son of a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate, a brave warrior of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a twisted\Nway of putting things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the undeniable\Nproof of his savage blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You run around spouting lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and act violent whenever you're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, you cozy\Nup to the lady of this house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can get her fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I only--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that your father is a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is more than enough proof\Nthat you'd hatch such a scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you still won't let up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore isn't a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just trying too hard\Nto do what's best for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never come near this mansion again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never come back here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid butt-ler jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain's not that kind of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! You stupid-head!\N--Stupid-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you saying it, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's your problem?!\N--Hey, now! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let go! You stupid butler!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come fight me, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will leave at once, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your meal, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cook would be sad\Nto hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He works his hardest to come up\Nwith meals that suit your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was wrong to talk with\NUsopp-san without telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't need to\Nkick him out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been nearly three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since the day I came to this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget what\Nhappened that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kicked off the ship I worked on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of a blunder I made,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with no work or money,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the verge\Nof dying like a beggar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! This is no place\Nfor the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Sir?! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! Take him\Ninside and tend to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:10:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my eyes, I owe my life\Nto your late parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to you, their daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that it isn't my place\Nto interfere with your friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Usopp lad isn't exactly\Nknown for his upstanding character!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... if anything should happen to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never be able to ask for\Nforgiveness from your kind parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think ill of me\Nfor what I did earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to have you, too, Klahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san is a very nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, whether he's\Nnice or not is irrelevant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore! Urgh! You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, "blockhead" will do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where'd Luffy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Probably\Nran after that "captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain would be at his spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always goes there\Nwhen something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nah, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But never mind that,\Nisn't one of you missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, Onion!\N--Yeah, Onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always just ups and disappears!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And then he\Nshows up all freaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See?\N--A b-backwards guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weird guy is\Nbackwards-walking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Liar!\N--Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who's calling me a weird guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seem pretty weird to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an ordinary,\Npassing-by hypnotist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hypnotist?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to\Nreveal my techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to a bunch of strangers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright. Watch this ring closely.\N--You're gonna do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel sleepy at the\Ncount of "one, two, Jango."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you!\NAt least say something, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what, do you want something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,insulting my old man like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hate that guy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says,\NYasopp was a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age where\Npirates are everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of my old man for living\Nwith his life on the line at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, that bastard\Nstomped all over my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not gonna\Ngo see the girl anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that butler comes and apologizes\Nto me, I might consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that butler doing out here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jango.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to avoid doing\Nanything to make you stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you go and sleep in\Nthe middle of the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand out one bit.\NI'm not weird, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone else\Nwith him. A weird guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen him before. Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, preparations for the\Nplan are ready, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can start anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rich Girl Assassination Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Assassination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it assassination, Jango.\NThat has a bad ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Accident. It's an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're those\Nguys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't look at me!\NThat's what I'd like to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't simply kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaya must perish\Nin an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, on your signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the men and I storm\Nthe village and kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll get her inheritance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You don't\Nunderstand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I, an outsider,\Ninherit Kaya's estate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll work hard to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard won't amount to squat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, this is the\Nmost important thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you kill her, you'll use\Nhypnosis to make Kaya write her will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to say, "I leave my entire\Nfortune to my butler, Klahadore!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then will I inherit\Nher enormous fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a completely ordinary manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent three long years gaining\Nthe trust of everyone around me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that it would be unsurprising for\Nher to leave her inheritance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years as a butler for that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure scared us back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, you suddenly said\Nyou were giving up life as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In no time flat, you set up\Na subordinate to be your double,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then let the world see\NCaptain Kuro get executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was the very\Nbeginning of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are Kuro,\NMan of a Thousand Plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I abandoned that\Nname three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now want to obtain\Ngreat sums of money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without the government on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I'm a pacifist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some pacifist you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,killing off an entire rich family\Nfor this "peace" of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now.\NThe father's death was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't planned on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, hurry and give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been sitting in the waters\Nnear here for a whole week now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The men are starting\Nto grow impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We heard\Nsomething really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?\NThis sounds kind of bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening\Nthis whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is seriously bad!\NThey're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuro is said\Nto be the smartest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most brutal pirate of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Word had it the navy caught and\Nexecuted him three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Captain Kuro is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Klahadore, the butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been after Kaya's fortune\Nfor these past three years straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna attack the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya's in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad! This is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't stand up! They'll see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Don't attack that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! They spotted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and hide before they kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... If it isn't Usopp-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They spotted me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Whatever do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here now, so of\Ncourse we didn't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We heard everything!\N--Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!\NWatch this ring closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is bad!\NIt's a throwing weapon! Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the count of "one, two,\NJango" you will get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One, two...\N--Hide! He's gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wake up, Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you still not\Nfixed that habit yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What're you doing?!\NYou're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head-first...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he couldn't have\Nsurvived from that height...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the other one?\NShall I take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what he does,\Nit won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, Jango.\NAttack the village at daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear up the villagers'\Nhomes a good amount,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make certain Miss Kaya's\Nmurder looks like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me, Usopp-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you\Ncan do to stop my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. My plans are flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, this is bad, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in this village I grew\Nup in is going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya's going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I love them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp!\NA brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've been unhappy lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cheer you up with a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave! I'll call for someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then? What happened after that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought, of course! Bravely, at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, for the giant cat,\NI used a cattail plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp ran by with a really\Nintense look. Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That butler is a pirate!\NHe told his crew to attack the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.61,0:24:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they'll know, and can run\Naway beforehand! That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no!\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to stock up on food\Nbefore the meat shop guy runs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.32,0:24:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue at hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.39,0:24:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.79,0:24:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Expose the Plot!\NPirate Butler Captain Kuro"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
